|:-------------------|------------:|-------:|
|&nbsp; Death Knight | 4d4 x 10 gp | 100 gp |
|&nbsp; Demon Hunter | 2d4 x 10 gp |  50 gp |
|&nbsp; Druid        | 2d4 x 10 gp |  50 gp |
